headline: Comcast Celebrates Dothan with New Peanut Sculptures
summary: In a celebration of local pride and community spirit, Comcast unveiled two new peanut sculptures as part of Dothan's iconic "Peanuts Around Town" public art project. The event, held at the Xfinity Store at 557 S Oates St, introduced two whimsical peanuts, one representing Xfinity and the other representing Comcast Business, as playful tributes to the company's services and Dothan's proud peanut heritage.
